{"tid":1573649,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"夏佳理：倫交所或隨時改變主意 收購仍有一線機會","createTime":"2019-09-16T05:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T11:44:06.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7bff4aadf2f93007ac674e7b64e03bc8fdcbf697","tid":1573649,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"倫交所拒絕港交所 (<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUzob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=84964001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>) 的收購提議，市場對於「世紀大刁」亦普遍不看好，惟港交所前主席夏佳理接受《彭博》訪問時表示，該收購是一單非常複雜的交易，但強調主席史美倫及行政總裁李小加在收購方面是相當有經驗的人，特別是李小加，他會懂得在倫敦的監管機構及金融圈子游刃。<br />\n<br />\n對於有消息指，港交所未來數周與倫交所股東會面，冀爭取收購成功，而敵意收購的機會亦可能增加，夏佳理表示，不排除倫交所會隨時改變主意，認為其留有一線機會。因在拒絕信件中提到收購要約低估了倫交所，意味著英國對收購的大門仍然未關上。而香港政府持有港交所5-6%股權，夏佳理認為不是大數目。他又指出，雙方合併後交易時段長達18小時，對亞洲和歐洲都有利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.965771/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.965771%2F2&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUzob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=587aa9d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.965771/2</a>"},{"pid":"649baf40e4480c36425df60714d59d7aa9cc18fe","tid":1573649,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"ef369e7ef9ddc7e509c410ccb2731420e0c17d9a","tid":1573649,"uid":161457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"唔好打咁多飛機"},{"pid":"f2d83c17325bf29383164a91d910248044cc97ea","tid":1573649,"uid":33099,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5zZB1K.png\" data-thumbna